            <abstract lang="en">
                <p>When a merchant desires to offer a promotion, the merchant suitably constructs and activates the bonus point promotion rule in real-time by utilizing the centralized promotions engine. When a consumer purchases the applicable products at the merchant, the promotion engine evaluates the consumer ID and consumer purchase data from a point of sale (POS) terminal, awards applicable promotions in real-time, and notifies the consumer of the promotion in real-time while the consumer is waiting at the POS terminal during check-out.</p>
